Don't be a douche, spellcheck.
DOUBLE CHECK YOUR INFO. If you're posting for old versions please list the version on the page and edit. For route pages, include Pokémon.
For dungeons, include Pokémon AND EVOLUTIONS
For egg pages, include ALL Pokémon preferably by bullet list (separated by region)
If you don't know the full info for an item/egg/route please do not edit the page.
